<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
    xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
    xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
    tal:omit-tag="textual">
<head tal:omit-tag="textual">
    <title tal:omit-tag="textual">Password Reset Request</title>
</head>
<body tal:omit-tag="textual">
    <h1 tal:omit-tag="textual">Password Reset Request</h1>
    
    <p tal:omit-tag="textual">Hello <span tal:replace="user" tal:condition="exists:user">User's Name</span>,</p>
    
    <p tal:omit-tag="textual">You have asked for a new password on the platform <span tal:replace="site_name">Site Name</span>. Please click on the following URL <a href="${reset_url}" tal:attributes="href reset_url">Reset Password Link</a> and provide your new password.</p>
    
    <p tal:omit-tag="textual">If you did not request this password reset, please ignore this email or contact support if you have any questions.</p>
    
    <p tal:omit-tag="textual">Best regards,</p>
    <p tal:omit-tag="textual">The team of <span tal:replace="site_name">Site Name</span></p>
</body>
</html>